pydmd.dmdc.DMDc._fit_B_known¶

DMDc._fit_B_known(X, Y, B)[source]¶

Private method that performs the dynamic mode decomposition algorithm with control when the matrix B is provided.

Parameters:
  • X (numpy.ndarray) – the first matrix of original snapshots.
  • Y (numpy.ndarray) – the second matrix of original snapshots.
  • I (numpy.ndarray) – the input control matrix.
  • B (numpy.ndarray) – the matrib B.
